company_name: VERLAG UND DRUCKEREI GERHARD BABICK INHABER NORBERT BABICK
information: The company VERLAG UND DRUCKEREI GERHARD BABICK INHABER NORBERT BABICK, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1952, which operates in the Flowering plants industry. It also operates in the Green-leaf plants industries. It is based in Pinneberg, Germany.
